OL,6,FThe UK could have a record six days
OL,7,Fof 30C heat for the first time in
OL,8,FSeptember
OL,10,FSaturday is provisionally the hottest
OL,11,Fday of the year so far, with 32.7C
OL,12,Frecorded in Heathrow.
OL,14,FThe UK has now sweltered through six
OL,15,Fdays of temperatures above 30C in
OL,16,FSeptember for the first time.
OL,18,FBut thunderstorms could spoil further
OL,19,Fspells of warm weather generated by
OL,20,Fthe record heatwave this weekend, the
OL,21,FMet Office has said.
OL,3,CTemperatures hit 32.7C on hottest day
OL,4,Cof the year so far
